cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a novel method for continual learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The method involves parameter decomposition and updating only task-specific parameters, which are factorized into sparse low-rank matrices. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the following sub-categories: 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning)
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence)
- cs.CV (Computer Vision)
- cs.CL (Computation and Language)
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing)
